folder: Columbia Heights & Cranberry Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
62-64 Columbia Heights, west side, opposite Cranberry St.(seen in the foreground.) This is a set of two views. No. 2 shows the Borough Hall section of Brooklyn in the background.

April 4, 1932
View 2: April 5, 1938

P.L. Sperr
No Reproductions.
